doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    title Urban Insight Inc. | Reset Password
  body(style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif")
    div(style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px")
      h1(style="text-align: center; color: #333333") Reset Your Password
      p(style="text-align: center; color: #777777; margin-top: 20px") You have requested to reset your password. Please click the button below to proceed.

      div(style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px")
        a(
          href="#",
          style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #9333ea; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px"
        ) Reset Password

      p(style="text-align: center; color: #777777; margin-top: 20px") If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.

      p(style="text-align: center; color: #777777; margin-top: 20px") If the button above does not work, you can copy and paste the following link into your web browser:
      p(
        style="text-align: center; color: #777777; margin-top: 10px; font-size: 12px"
      ) #{ resetLink }

      p(style="text-align: center; color: #777777; margin-top: 20px") Regards,
      p(style="text-align: center; color: #777777") Urban Insight Inc.
